ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整多個object member<br />\n代番個名入去就得<br />\nruntime轉object名好似就冇辦法</blockquote><br />\nfor example?"},{"pid":"fc3831092926fdce6bb8c4d9644e57d7d585f3de","tid":147821,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整多個object member<br />\n代番個名入去就得<br />\nruntime轉object名好似就冇辦法</blockquote><br />\nfor example?</blockquote><br />\nclass member先啱<br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa50d57a63f28029cd783bd7de602c37aac5a5a","tid":147821,"uid":61249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"c++本來就係static type language, 乜都要compile 前知晒D class, 從而提升個program 執行速度。Dynamic object creation 要靠reflection 做。c++ 唔係做唔到、但會無左個原意囉。<br />\n<br />\n如果個input 唔係太random, 你可以用if then else 去做、或者OO化D、用factory pattern 去做<br />\n<br />\neg.<br />\nif (input == 'Peter') return new Peter();<br />\nif (input == 'Mary) return new Mary();"},{"pid":"f660620468f1e009e319058c1177df5e08e7deae","tid":147821,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T13:35:30.000Z","msg":"明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔好意思唔知點表達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝各位巴打"},{"pid":"90dea3f9b6c1e58088bae829422d3d0132f7fb39","tid":147821,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T08:31:28.000Z","msg":"最後用左vector解決"},{"pid":"5d5602358a8ef35f4510d516fb203b8e3339b56c","tid":147821,"uid":65030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最後用左vector解決</blockquote><br />\n點解決"},{"pid":"31430153b4b5c6580a204b4e7c4613d54709a13b","tid":147821,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最後用左vector解決</blockquote><br />\n點解決</blockquote><br />\n我覺得樓主嗰個係xy problem入面既y problem<br />\n好想知佢個x problem係乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dad4cd65174d055a278d9189f0cf4d8fe100a0b","tid":147821,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:18:04.000Z","msg":"我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得只為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type"},{"pid":"fda98dad9073cc35b8a4f52693ea29862c30b143","tid":147821,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T15:18:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得*因為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type</blockquote>"},{"pid":"b35b23c8e85918505dfb5cb4b444a038601cab09","tid":147821,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:27:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得*因為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁關你原本條問題咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔係好明你唔用得array個原因，關datatype咩事？"},{"pid":"1bc43d5170f7cc11e26af58a594de89a62e2b768","tid":147821,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得*因為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁關你原本條問題咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔係好明你唔用得array個原因，關datatype咩事？</blockquote><br />\nArray 只可以放同一個data type嘅野<br />\n我係想program入面run緊果時可以整多個object"},{"pid":"836dff9e6cb19c2f78671fd1a0d0cc5895a9ae4d","tid":147821,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:30:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得*因為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁關你原本條問題咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔係好明你唔用得array個原因，關datatype咩事？</blockquote><br />\nArray 只可以放同一個data type嘅野<br />\n我係想program入面run緊果時可以整多個object</blockquote><br />\n咁你vector&lt;Account&gt; 都淨係可以放Account呢種type既objects"},{"pid":"d57ae354e6ecf70915dcef189f7f15d2b7ef3445","tid":147821,"uid":36823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T02:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想整一個program<br />\n係可以比人整新account去store野<br />\nArray唔得*因為store野係有唔同datatype<br />\n所以就用vector&lt;Account&gt; <br />\n用class嚟做data type</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咁關你原本條問題咩事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔係好明你唔用得array個原因，關datatype咩事？</blockquote><br />\nArray 只可以放同一個data type嘅野<br />\n我係想program入面run緊果時可以整多個object</blockquote><br />\n咁你vector&lt;Account&gt; 都淨係可以放Account呢種type既objects</blockquote><br />\n係囉 一樣淨係放到一個data type<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實樓主個問題分兩個部份<br />\n1: 將唔同data type嘅嘢store埋做一個Account<br />\n2: 想有一個dynamic size array去比人runtime create/delete Accounts同埋store住啲Accounts<br />\n<br />\n1就開Account class去store住啲information<br />\n2就用vector去store住啲Account objects<br />\n<br />\n假設Account個class define咗constructor, 應該大概係咁寫:<br />\nvector&lt;Account&gt; accounts;<br />\nAccount * account;<br />\nstring name;<br />\ngetline(cin,name);<br />\naccount = new Account(name);"}]}